---
const pages = [
  { label: 'Home',             href: '/',               external: false },
  { label: 'About',            href: '/about',           external: false },
  { label: 'Blog',             href: '/blog',            external: false },
  { label: 'Contact',          href: '/contact',         external: false },
  { label: 'Privacy Policy',   href: 'https://www.notion.so/Unify-s-Privacy-Policy-2e15af89dddb80b0b37ee497e6d4e38c?source=copy_link', external: true },
  { label: 'Terms of Service', href: 'https://www.notion.so/Unify-s-End-User-License-Agreement-Terms-of-Service-3185af89dddb80a68410fa8d65d615c7?source=copy_link', external: true },
];

const social = [
  { label: 'Instagram', href: 'https://www.instagram.com/unifysocial.ca/'                                        },
  { label: 'Facebook',  href: 'https://www.facebook.com/p/Unify-Social-61570879043328/'                          },
  { label: 'LinkedIn',  href: 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/unify-social/posts/?feedView=all'                },
  { label: 'Twitter',   href: 'https://x.com/unifysocialca'                                                      },
];
---

<footer class="bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-layout px-6 desktop:px-10 pt-16 pb-10">

    <!-- Heading with brand-red left border -->
    <div class="footer-heading mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-marquee text-ink leading-tight">
        Unify,<br />
        Your journey to Canada, <em>simplified.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Two-column body: description left, links right -->
    <div class="flex flex-col tablet:flex-row gap-12 tablet:gap-16 mb-16">

      <!-- Left: brand description -->
      <div class="flex-1 max-w-2xl">
        <p class="font-display text-text text-base leading-relaxed">
          Newcomers to Canada are expected to navigate life in a new country, yet many face a maze of disconnected resources, complex processes, and limited access to community. While support exists, there is no central digital platform that brings trusted information, guidance, and human connection together in one place.
        </p>
        <p class="font-display text-text text-base leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Unify is a digital platform designed to support newcomers by centralizing essential resources, providing step-by-step guidance, and fostering meaningful community connections. The platform includes five core features: Learn, offering curated content on essential topics, an AI Companion that provides personalized, 24/7 guidance; a Personalized Settlement Checklist that organizes tasks based on each user's goals and status; a Community layer with Q&amp;A forums, interest and cultural groups, and a local events calendar; and Community Meets, which help newcomers build real relationships. Together, Unify reduces confusion, builds confidence, and ensures newcomers never have to navigate their settlement journey alone.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Pages + Socials -->
      <div class="flex gap-12 tablet:gap-16 flex-shrink-0">

        <!-- Pages -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-ink text-sm tracking-wide uppercase mb-5">
            Pages
          </h3>
          <ul role="list" class="list-none m-0 p-0 flex flex-col gap-3">
            {pages.map(({ label, href, external }) => (
              <li>
                <a
                  href={href}
                  class="font-display text-blue-600 text-sm hover:underline"
                  target={external ? '_blank' : undefined}
                  rel={external ? 'noopener noreferrer' : undefined}
                >
                  {label}
                </a>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Socials -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-ink text-sm tracking-wide uppercase mb-5">
            Socials
          </h3>
          <ul role="list" class="list-none m-0 p-0 flex flex-col gap-3">
            {social.map(({ label, href }) => (
              <li>
                <a
                  href={href}
                  class="font-display text-blue-600 text-sm hover:underline"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >
                  {label}
                </a>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom bar -->
    <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-6">
      <a
        href="https://unifysocial.ca"
        class="font-display text-sm text-blue-600 hover:underline"
      >
        © 2026 – Unify Social
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer-heading {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-brand);
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
</style>
